+/*---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
+ *  RemotePair: "Terminal" sidebar container that embeds a real EditorPart so its
+ *  content is editor-tab-based (horizontal tabs), terminal-specialized.
+ *
+ *  Two conditions (per design): (1) it IS a primary-sidebar view container that the
+ *  activity-bar rail switches with the file "Browser"; (2) inside it lives a real
+ *  EditorPart (editor tabs), not a vertical list. VS Code has no native "editor
+ *  group inside a sidebar", so we instantiate a standalone EditorPart (same machine
+ *  AuxiliaryEditorPart uses for auxiliary windows) and mount it into a ViewPane body.
+ *--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
