+	/**
+	 * Open a new terminal as an editor inside the embedded EditorPart's own group.
+	 * Using the part's `activeGroup` (not a scoped IEditorService) keeps the editor
+	 * inside the embedded part instead of leaking into the main editor area.
+	 */
